# E Details of Fine-Tuning

We fine-tune LLaMA-3.1-8B-Instruct using LLaMA-Factory [\(Zheng et al.,](#page-11-0) [2024\)](#page-11-0), setting the number of epochs to 1 and the learning rate to 1e-4. We adopt a LoRA strategy [\(Hu et al.\)](#page-9-16) instead of training with full parameters, as we observe the latter method often leads to the model outputting the same answer for all test samples. Fine-tuning is performed on two NVIDIA A800 GPUs, taking roughly 15 minutes.


